    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade BMW E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its analog purity. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-redline delivery that remains crisp and responsive. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a professional VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The six-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under load. The exterior retains its factory-original luster, while the cabin shows no signs of typical bolster wear or trim delamination. Mechanically flawless and cosmetically pristine, this M3 is a turn-key specimen for the serious collector.",
